  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">National Financial vehicle - Burkina Green Energy funds</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The PIN is to seek approval to support the GoBF to develop a National Financial Vehicule in Burkina Faso and increase their opportunity to have access to climate finance, especially in Renewable energy and energy efficiency.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to support the Government of Burkina Faso (GoBF) during its Green Growth transition by developing a financial mechanism that enables private investment, particularly in renewable energy and energy efficiency sector,  as well as capacity development of key stakeholders. The major output of this project is to develop a National Financial Vehicle that will integrate the minimum requirementn to facilitate access to climate finance.</narrative>
  </description>
